node.title: 'Multiple' people escape from Howard Springs COVID quarantine facility near Darwin
node.alt: Aerials drone pics of Howard Springs Quarantine Facility.
node.description: Police have descended on the Howard Springs quarantine facility near Darwin, where they say "multiple" people have escaped.
node.content: ["Northern Territory Police say \"multiple\"\u00a0people have\u00a0escaped from Darwin's Howard Springs COVID-19 quarantine facility.", "A large number of police officers are currently at the scene.", "Officers in masks are searching vehicles in the area.", "Staff at the facility are conducting a headcount of those staying in the centre.", "More to come."]
